summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department; authorizing the preparation of plans, specifications and cost estimates for the rehabilitation of the Airport Way S. Viaduct over Argo Railroad Yards, and making a partially reimbursable appropriation from the Seattle General Street Improvement Bonds 1960 Fund therefor, and in connection therewith authorizing an agreement with the State of Washington, Department of Highways, for financial assistance under the Federal Highway Administration "Special Bridge Replacement Program".
